data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This spacious 5 bedroom, 3 full bath residence is nestled on a generous level lot with a beautifully FENCED BACKYARD, providing you with the perfect oasis for your family. Enjoy the serenity of the outdoors on your COVERED PATIO, where evenings come alive around the fire pit.    On the main level, you'll find a convenient FULL BEDROOM and FULL BATH, ideal for hosting guests. Whether you work from home or simply love to entertain, the formal dining room and formal living room offer versatile spaces for your needs. The heart of the home is the chef's kitchen, complete with GRANITE countertops and an open-concept design that seamlessly flows into the living room. HARDWOOD FLOORS THROUGHOUT the main level add a touch of elegance.    Upstairs, discover four additional bedrooms and a spacious MEDIA ROOM, providing ample space for all your entertainment needs. The generous owner's retreat is large enough for a cozy sitting area, allowing you to escape into your own world with a good book or quiet reflection.    This home boasts a 3-CAR GARAGE and showcases fresh NEW EXTERIOR PAINT, making it a true standout in the neighborhood. Move-in ready, it's your opportunity to make this your forever home. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity - come and experience the epitome of comfortable, modern living!
